select t.* from (
Select null AccNo, null Value2, d.DocNo, d.DebitAccountNo, d.CreditAccountNo, d.OperDate, d.Device, d.EntCode,
       d.EntType, d.PAN, d.MBR, d.Term, d.TermLocation, d.OrgCurrency, d.OrgValue, d.Currency,
       d.SICCode, d.Value, d.TranCode, d.Approval, d.Retailer, d.TermCountry, d.TermCity,
       d.AcctImpactList, d.RollbackData, d.AcquirerFIID, d.IncPSFields, d.AdditionalFields, d.MessToCardHolder
  From tExtractDelay d
  Where d.Branch = :B
    and d.DebitAccountNo = :A
    And (d.DocNo Is Null or d.DocNo > :DN)
    And nvl(d.OrgCurrency, -1) = nvl(:OC, nvl(d.OrgCurrency, -1))
    And d.Value >= .01
    And d.OperDate Between nvl(:DF, d.OperDate) And nvl(:DT, d.OperDate)
union all
Select null AccNo, null Value2, d.DocNo, d.DebitAccountNo, d.CreditAccountNo, d.OperDate, d.Device, d.EntCode,
       d.EntType, d.PAN, d.MBR, d.Term, d.TermLocation, d.OrgCurrency, d.OrgValue, d.Currency,
       d.SICCode, d.Value, d.TranCode, d.Approval, d.Retailer, d.TermCountry, d.TermCity,
       d.AcctImpactList, d.RollbackData, d.AcquirerFIID, d.IncPSFields, d.AdditionalFields, d.MessToCardHolder
  From tExtractDelay d
  Where d.Branch = :B
    and d.CreditAccountNo = :A
    and SubStr(d.RollbackData, 1, 1) = 'B'
    And (d.DocNo Is Null or d.DocNo > :DN)
    And nvl(d.OrgCurrency, -1) = nvl(:OC, nvl(d.OrgCurrency, -1))
    And d.Value >= .01
    And d.OperDate Between nvl(:DF, d.OperDate) And nvl(:DT, d.OperDate)
union all
Select dl.AccountNo AccNo, dl.Value Value2, d.DocNo, d.DebitAccountNo, d.CreditAccountNo, d.OperDate, d.Device, d.EntCode,
       d.EntType, d.PAN, d.MBR, d.Term, d.TermLocation, d.OrgCurrency, d.OrgValue, d.Currency,
       d.SICCode, d.Value, d.TranCode, d.Approval, d.Retailer, d.TermCountry, d.TermCity,
       d.AcctImpactList, d.RollbackData, d.AcquirerFIID, d.IncPSFields, d.AdditionalFields, d.MessToCardHolder
  From tExtractDelayList dl, tExtractDelay d
  Where dl.Branch = :B
    and dl.AccountNo = :A
    and d.Branch = dl.Branch
    and d.PackNo = dl.PackNo
    and d.RecNo = dl.RecNo
    And (d.DocNo Is Null or d.DocNo > :DN)
    And nvl(d.OrgCurrency, -1) = nvl(:OC, nvl(d.OrgCurrency, -1))
    And d.Value >= .01
    And d.OperDate Between nvl(:DF, d.OperDate) And nvl(:DT, d.OperDate)
) t Order by 6 desc

begin 
/*
  Пуск -> 
    Настройки -> 
      Внешние онлайн-интерфейсы -> 
        Входящий  интерфейс CoreBanking -> 
          Выписка по онлайн-запросу (GetStatement) -> 
            Блок предобработки запроса -> 
              PL/SQL блок.
          
*/
/*
 Дата       Автор           Описание
 ---------- --------------- ----------------------------------------------------
 01.02.2019 Скадовский А.А. [18-55682] Выписка по кредитному счету                      
 28.07.2021 Скадовский А.А. CREDCARD-607 Отображать клиенту в разделе "История операций" в МБ только сумму фактически понесенных расходов на покупки
*/
/* Скрипт схлопывает операции по кодам из таблицы ubrr_saa_statement_groupcode*/
declare
  pParams     RPC.TypeStatementParams := RPC.GetStatementInfo_Params();   -- входящие параметры запроса
  pOperTypes  types.ArrNum            := RPC.GetStatementInfo_OperList(); -- входящий список операций
  pAttrList   types.ArrStr100         := RPC.GetStatementInfo_AttrList(); -- входящий список параметров
  vOutList    RPC.TypeStatementList;  
  vErr        number;
  vBranch     number := seance.getbranch;
 
  procedure ChangeOutList is
    pragma autonomous_transaction;
    i binary_integer;
    l_acc varchar2 (20);
    cursor cNewList is
    select *
      from (select *
              from ubrr_saa_getstatement s
             where not exists (select 1
                                 from ubrr_saa_statement_groupcode g
                                where g.code = s.entrycode 
                                  and g.branch = vBranch)
             union all
            select max (frontid)          frontid
                 , max (backid)            backid
                 , operdate
                 , max (code)              code
                 , sum (amount)            amount
                 , max (description)       description
                 , max (type)              type
                 , max (trantime)          trantime
                 , max (pan)               pan
                 , max (mbr)               mbr
                 , max (termclass)         termclass
                 , max (termname)          termname
                 , max (termlocation)      termlocation
                 , max (termsic)           termsic
                 , max (termcountry)       termcountry
                 , max (termcity)          termcity
                 , max (origamount)        origamount
                 , max (origcurrency)      origcurrency
                 , max (anothertitle)      anothertitle
                 , max (backaccount)       backaccount
                 , sum (backamount)        backamount
                 , sum (remain)            remain
                 , max (approval)          approval
                 , max (currency)          currency
                 , max (account)           account
                 , max (retailername)      retailername
                 , max (fullremark)        fullremark
                 , max (acctimpactlist)    acctimpactlist
                 , entrycode
                 , creditaccount
              from ubrr_saa_getstatement s
             where exists (select 1
                             from ubrr_saa_statement_groupcode g
                            where g.code = s.entrycode 
                              and g.branch = vBranch)
             group by entrycode, operdate, creditaccount)
     order by backid, operdate;
    procedure set_record (
      pRec RPC.TypeStatementRecord) is
      l_rec ubrr_saa_getstatement%rowtype;
      cursor cAcc (pAcc varchar2) is      
      select /*+ ALL_ROWS */ e.CreditAccount
        from tEntry e 
       where e.branch       = vBranch                 
         and e.docno        = pRec.backid       
         and e.debitaccount = pAcc              
         and e.debitentcode = pRec.EntryCode    
         and e.value        = abs (pRec.Amount) 
       order by no;
      cursor cAcc45509 (pAcc varchar2) is      
      select /*+ ALL_ROWS */ '1' 
        from tEntry e 
       where e.branch        = vBranch                 
         and e.docno         = pRec.backid       
         and e.debitaccount  like '45509%'       
         and e.creditaccount = pAcc               
         and e.debitentcode  = pRec.EntryCode
         and e.value         = abs (pRec.Amount);
      cursor cIsGroup is
      select '1'
        from ubrr_saa_statement_groupcode g
       where g.code   = pRec.EntryCode
         and g.branch = vBranch;
      l_dummy char(1);
    begin
      l_rec.FrontId         :=  pRec.FrontId       ;
      l_rec.BackId          :=  pRec.BackId        ;
      l_rec.OperDate        :=  pRec.OperDate      ;
      l_rec.Code            :=  pRec.Code          ;
      l_rec.Amount          :=  pRec.Amount        ;
      l_rec.Description     :=  pRec.Description   ;
      l_rec.Type            :=  pRec.Type          ;
      l_rec.TranTime        :=  pRec.TranTime      ;
      l_rec.PAN             :=  pRec.PAN           ;
      l_rec.MBR             :=  pRec.MBR           ;
      l_rec.TermClass       :=  pRec.TermClass     ;
      l_rec.TermName        :=  pRec.TermName      ;
      l_rec.TermLocation    :=  pRec.TermLocation  ;
      l_rec.TermSIC         :=  pRec.TermSIC       ;
      l_rec.TermCountry     :=  pRec.TermCountry   ;
      l_rec.TermCity        :=  pRec.TermCity      ;
      l_rec.OrigAmount      :=  pRec.OrigAmount    ;
      l_rec.OrigCurrency    :=  pRec.OrigCurrency  ;
      l_rec.AnotherTitle    :=  pRec.AnotherTitle  ;
      l_rec.BackAccount     :=  pRec.BackAccount   ;
      l_rec.BackAmount      :=  pRec.BackAmount    ;
      l_rec.Remain          :=  pRec.Remain        ;
      l_rec.Approval        :=  pRec.Approval      ;
      l_rec.Currency        :=  pRec.Currency      ;
      l_rec.Account         :=  pRec.Account       ;
      l_rec.RetailerName    :=  pRec.RetailerName  ;
      l_rec.FullRemark      :=  pRec.FullRemark    ;
      l_rec.AcctImpactList  :=  pRec.AcctImpactList;
      l_rec.EntryCode       :=  pRec.EntryCode     ;
      open cIsGroup;
      fetch cIsGroup into l_dummy;
      if cIsGroup%found then
        l_acc := ubrr_get_account423 (pRec.Account);
        open cAcc (l_acc);
        fetch cAcc into l_rec.CreditAccount;
        close cAcc;
      end if;
      close cIsGroup;
      if l_rec.EntryCode = 1 then
        l_acc := ubrr_get_account423 (pRec.BackAccount);
        open cAcc45509 (l_acc);
        fetch cAcc45509 into l_dummy;
        if cAcc45509%found then
          close cAcc45509;
          return;
        end if;
        close cAcc45509;
      end if;
      insert into a4m.ubrr_saa_getstatement values l_rec;
    end;
    function get_record (
      pRec ubrr_saa_getstatement%rowtype) 
      return RPC.TypeStatementRecord is
      l_rec RPC.TypeStatementRecord;
    begin
      l_rec.FrontId         :=  pRec.FrontId       ;
      l_rec.BackId          :=  pRec.BackId        ;
      l_rec.OperDate        :=  pRec.OperDate      ;
      l_rec.Code            :=  pRec.Code          ;
      l_rec.Amount          :=  pRec.Amount        ;
      l_rec.Description     :=  pRec.Description   ;
      l_rec.Type            :=  pRec.Type          ;
      l_rec.TranTime        :=  pRec.TranTime      ;
      l_rec.PAN             :=  pRec.PAN           ;
      l_rec.MBR             :=  pRec.MBR           ;
      l_rec.TermClass       :=  pRec.TermClass     ;
      l_rec.TermName        :=  pRec.TermName      ;
      l_rec.TermLocation    :=  pRec.TermLocation  ;
      l_rec.TermSIC         :=  pRec.TermSIC       ;
      l_rec.TermCountry     :=  pRec.TermCountry   ;
      l_rec.TermCity        :=  pRec.TermCity      ;
      l_rec.OrigAmount      :=  pRec.OrigAmount    ;
      l_rec.OrigCurrency    :=  pRec.OrigCurrency  ;
      l_rec.AnotherTitle    :=  pRec.AnotherTitle  ;
      l_rec.BackAccount     :=  pRec.BackAccount   ;
      l_rec.BackAmount      :=  pRec.BackAmount    ;
      l_rec.Remain          :=  pRec.Remain        ;
      l_rec.Approval        :=  pRec.Approval      ;
      l_rec.Currency        :=  pRec.Currency      ;
      l_rec.Account         :=  pRec.Account       ;
      l_rec.RetailerName    :=  pRec.RetailerName  ;
      l_rec.FullRemark      :=  pRec.FullRemark    ;
      l_rec.AcctImpactList  :=  pRec.AcctImpactList;
      l_rec.EntryCode       :=  pRec.EntryCode     ;
      return l_rec;
    end;
  begin
    execute immediate 'truncate table a4m.ubrr_saa_getstatement';
    i := vOutList.first;
    while i is not null loop
      set_record (vOutList(i));
      i := vOutList.next (i);
    end loop;
    commit;
    vOutList.delete;
    
    for r in cNewList loop 
      vOutList (vOutList.count + 1) := get_record (r); 
    end loop;
  end;  
begin
  vOutList.delete;
  vErr := StatementTWO.GetStatement (
    pParams
  , pOperTypes
  , pAttrList
  , vOutList);
  ChangeOutList;
  RPC.SetStatementInfo(vOutList);
  :RET := 1; 
end;
 null; end;

SELECT /*+ rule */ MAX(OPDATE), NVL(SUM(VALUE),0) 
FROM
 (SELECT D.OPDATE, E.VALUE, E.DEBITENTCODE FROM TENTRY E, TDOCUMENT D WHERE 
  E.BRANCH = :B4 AND E.DEBITACCOUNT = :B3 AND E.DEBITENTCODE IN (2,126,128,
  130,132,135,136,138,141,142,143, 144,145,146,147,148,149,258,259,260,268,
  269, 270,271,272,273,274,275,276,277,280,281,282, 295,297,298,299,305,306,
  307,310,323,324, 474,477,479,480,494,495,251,252,253,278,279, 285,294,597,
  599,601,604,606,666) AND D.BRANCH = E.BRANCH AND D.DOCNO = E.DOCNO AND 
  D.NEWDOCNO IS NULL AND D.OPDATE BETWEEN :B2 +1 AND :B1 UNION ALL SELECT 
  D.OPDATE, E.VALUE, E.DEBITENTCODE FROM TENTRYARC E, TDOCUMENTARC D WHERE 
  E.BRANCH = :B4 AND E.DEBITACCOUNT = :B3 AND E.DEBITENTCODE IN (2,126,128,
  130,132,135,136,138,141,142,143, 144,145,146,147,148,149,258,259,260,268,
  269, 270,271,272,273,274,275,276,277,280,281,282, 295,297,298,299,305,306,

declare 
vOper OperKernel.TOper:=OperKernel.s_pOper; b boolean:=true; 
vObjType number := OperKernel.s_pObjType; 
vOperC    number := vOper.cOper; 
vData     varchar(3000) := OperKernel.s_pData; 
vSelf     boolean := OperKernel.s_pSelf; 
begin 
if vOper.evPre then 
  b:= ExchangeVISA.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 2, true, vData);
end if;
if b then 
  if vSelf  then 
    b:=ExchangeVISA.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  else 
    b:=Exchange.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  end if;
end if;
if vOper.evPost then 
  b:= ExchangeVISA.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 4, b, vData);
end if;
OperKernel.sBufBool:=b;
end;

begin 
declare
 vEntryRec      APITypes.TypeStatementEntryRecord;
 vIndent        tReferenceEntry.Ident%TYPE;
 vOperDetail    varchar2 (2000);
 vUpd           boolean := false;
datest date;
datefin date;
begin
 vEntryRec := StatementDataPrepare.GetCurrentRecord();  --Get current record
 vIndent := ReferenceEntry.GetIdent(vEntryRec.EntCode);
 --ubrr_log('VYP ON-LINE vIndent '||vIndent);
 --ubrr_log('VYP ON-LINE vIndent vEntryRec.OperDate '||to_char(vEntryRec.OperDate,'dd.mm.rrrr'));
 --ubrr_log('VYP ON-LINE vIndent vEntryRec.Value '||vEntryRec.Value);
 --ubrr_log('VYP ON-LINE vIndent vEntryRec.DocNo'||vEntryRec.DocNo);
 --ubrr_log('VYP ON-LINE vIndent vEntryRec.EntNo '||vEntryRec.EntNo);
--ubrr_log('VYP ON-LINE vIndent vEntryRec.TranCode '||vEntryRec.TranCode);
PRAGMA AUTONOMOUS_TRANSACTION;
datest :=  sysdate;
 if vIndent in ('ACC_IN') then 
     if UPPER (vEntryRec.FullRemark) like '%ZPL%' then 
         vOperDetail := 'Зачисление заработной платы '
                               ||NVL (to_char (vEntryRec.ValueDate, 'DD.MM.YYYY HH24:MI:SS'), ' ');
         vUpd := true;
     elsif vEntryRec.ShortRemark = '+' then 
         vOperDetail := 'Поступление денежных средств. '||NVL (vEntryRec.FullRemark, ' ')||' '||  
                                 NVL (to_char (vEntryRec.ValueDate, 'DD.MM.YYYY HH24:MI:SS'), ' ');
         vUpd := true;
     end if;
 elsif vIndent in ('ACC_ADD') and UPPER (vEntryRec.ShortRemark) = 'ИЗ ВКЛАДОВ' then 
     vOperDetail := NVL (vEntryRec.FullRemark, ' ')||' '||  
                    NVL (to_char (vEntryRec.ValueDate, 'DD.MM.YYYY HH24:MI:SS'), ' ');
     vUpd := true;
--->>> Нестеров И.В. 04.05.2013 - п.п. 12-1066
  elsif vIndent in ('OPEXT_A40','OPEXT_I51') then
      if vEntryRec.Value < 0 then 
        vOperDetail := 'На счет:'||ubrr_get_account408(vEntryRec.Account);
      elsif vEntryRec.Value > 0 then
        vOperDetail := 'Со счета:'||ubrr_get_account408(vEntryRec.Account);
  end if;
      vUpd := true;
--->>> Нестеров И.В. 04.05.2013 - п.п. 12-1066
 elsif (vIndent in ('ACC_OUT')) or (vIndent like 'OPCOM%' and UPPER (vEntryRec.ShortRemark) = 'КОМИССИЯ') then 
     declare
         v_name  tplanaccount.name%TYPE;
     begin
         select a.name
           into v_name
           from tentry       e
              , tplanaccount a
          where e.branch = 1
            and e.docno  = vEntryRec.DocNo
            and e.no     = vEntryRec.EntNo
            and e.branch = a.branch
            and ((e.debitaccount like '4230%'
                  and e.creditaccount = a.internal)
                 or (e.creditaccount like '4230%'
                     and e.debitaccount = a.internal)
                );
            
         vOperDetail := v_name;           
     exception
         when others then null;          
     end;
     vOperDetail := NVL (vOperDetail, ' ')||' '||NVL (to_char (vEntryRec.ValueDate, 'DD.MM.YYYY HH24:MI:SS'), ' ');
     vUpd := true;
     
 elsif vIndent like 'CLIENTCNSSERVICE_PAYMENT_FP%' and UPPER (vEntryRec.ShortRemark) = 'ПЛАТЕЖ' then   
     declare
         v_name  tplanaccount.name%TYPE;
     begin
         select a.name
           into v_name
           from tentry       e
              , tplanaccount a
          where e.branch = 1
            and e.docno  = vEntryRec.DocNo
            and e.no     = vEntryRec.EntNo
            and e.branch = a.branch
            and e.creditaccount = a.internal;
    
         vOperDetail := v_name;    
     exception
         when others then null;
     end;
     vOperDetail := NVL (vOperDetail, ' ')||' '||NVL (to_char (vEntryRec.ValueDate, 'DD.MM.YYYY HH24:MI:SS'), ' '); 
     vUpd := true;
           
 elsif vIndent = 'OPEXT_I69' and UPPER (vEntryRec.ShortRemark) = 'ДПЕРЕВОД' then     
     vOperDetail := 'Исходящий перевод, получатель ';
     
     declare
         v_accountno varchar2 (20);
         v_fio       varchar2 (40);
     begin
         select --+ rule
                e.creditaccountno, p.fio
           into v_accountno, v_fio   
           from textract  e
              , taccount  a
              , tclientpersone p
          where e.branch   = 1
            and e.trancode = vEntryRec.TranCode
            and e.branch   = a.branch
            and e.creditaccountno = a.accountno
            and a.branch   = p.branch
            and a.idclient = p.idclient;
            
            vOperDetail := vOperDetail||NVL (v_fio, ' ')||' '||NVL (v_accountno, ' ');          
     exception
         when others then null;
     end;   
     vUpd := true;  
 
 elsif vIndent = 'OPEXT_I70' and UPPER (vEntryRec.ShortRemark) = 'КПЕРЕВОД' then
     vOperDetail := 'Входящий перевод, плательщик: ';
     declare
         v_fio        varchar2 (40);
         v_accountno  varchar2 (20);
     /*begin
         select  p.fio, c.accountno
           into  v_fio, v_accountno

              ,  tclientpersone p

               into  v_fio, v_accountno
               from  tcustomer       c
                  ,  tclientpersone  p 
              where  c.branch     = 1
                and  c.customer   = vEntryRec.pan
                and  c.branch     = p.branch
                and  c.idclient   = p.idclient;

         exception
             when others then null;
         end; 
         /*when others then null;
     end;*/
     vUpd := true;
 
 elsif vIndent in ('OPEXT_I55', 'OPEXT_A63', 'OPEXT_P32') and UPPER (vEntryRec.ShortRemark) = 'ПЕРЕВОД-' then 
     vOperDetail := 'Исходящий перевод. '; 
    
     declare
         v_fio      varchar2 (40);
         v_pan      varchar2 (20);
     begin
         
         select  p.fio, c.pan
           into  v_fio, v_pan
           from  tcard           c
              ,  textract        e
              ,  tclientpersone  p 
          where  e.branch     = 1
            and  e.trancode   = vEntryRec.TranCode
            and  c.branch     = 1
            and  c.pan        = substr (e.userdata, 1, instr (e.userdata, '~')- 1)
            and  c.branch     = p.branch
            and  c.idclient   = p.idclient; 
            
         vOperDetail := vOperDetail||NVL (v_fio, ' ')||', '||substr (v_pan, 1, 4)||'********'||substr (v_pan, 13); 
         
     exception
         when others then null;          
     end;
     vUpd := true;
    
 elsif vIndent in ('OPEXT_I56', 'OPEXT_A64', 'OPEXT_P33') and UPPER (vEntryRec.ShortRemark) = 'ПЕРЕВОД+' then 
     vOperDetail := 'Входящий перевод. '; 
 
     declare
         v_fio      varchar2 (40);

     exception
         when others then null;
     end;
     vUpd := true;
ELSIF vIndent='OPEXT_P10' or vIndent='OPEXT_I52'/*'ACC_CASHBACK'*/ THEN
    --ubrr_log('VYP ON-LINE зашли в OPEXT_P10');
    BEGIN
      SELECT '#sumcb='||to_char((SUM_CASHBACK+SUM_UPCASHBACK),'FM9999990D00')
        INTO vOperDetail
        FROM UBRR_CNS_CASHBACK_DET
       WHERE DOC_NO=vEntryRec.docno;
    EXCEPTION WHEN OTHERS THEN 
      ubrr_log('VYP ON-LINE упали в OPEXT_P10/OPEXT_I52 vEntryRec.docno '||vEntryRec.docno);
    END;
/*   
  ELSIF vIndent='OPEXT_P10'/*'ACC_CASHBACK'*/ /*THEN

    vUpd := true;
  ELSIF vIndent='ACC_CASH_BACK' THEN
    vOperDetail:='#tp=ACC_CASH_BACK';
  ELSIF vIndent='PRC_EXT_CAP' THEN
    vOperDetail:='#tp=PRC_EXT_CAP';

  begin
    SELECT vOperDetail||'#mcc='||rg.ident||'#mccname='||rg.name
      into vOperDetail

           treferencegroupmcc rg
     WHERE g.branch=1 
       AND g.mcc=vEntryRec.SICCode
       AND rg.branch=g.branch
       AND rg.IDENT=g.IDENT;
  exception when others then 
    ubrr_log('VYP ON-LINE не получилось определить группы мсс');
  end;
  --->>> Шабанова Е.М. 06.03.2018 - п.п. 17-788.2 
  begin
    select  vOperDetail||'#entcode='|| tex.device ||' '|| tex.entcode
    into vOperDetail

    where tex.branch=1
    and tex.trancode   = vEntryRec.TranCode;
  exception when others then 
    ubrr_log('VYP ON-LINE не получилось определить группы мсс');
  end;
   ---<<< Шабанова Е.М. 06.03.2018 
  --->>> Лямцева Е.И. 13.02.2013 - п.п. 12-1066

     or substr(vEntryRec.Account,1,5) in ('42301','42601')

 if vUpd then

declare 
vOper OperKernel.TOper:=OperKernel.s_pOper; b boolean:=true;

begin

  b:= Twi.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 2, true, vData);

    b:=Twi.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);

    b:=Exchange.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  end if;
end if;

  b:= Twi.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 4, b, vData);
end if;
OperKernel.sBufBool:=b;
end;

declare 
vOper OperKernel.TOper:=OperKernel.s_pOper; b boolean:=true; 
vObjType number := OperKernel.s_pObjType; 
vOperC    number := vOper.cOper;

vSelf     boolean := OperKernel.s_pSelf; 
begin 
if vOper.evPre then 
  b:= ExchangeAnalyze.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 2, true, vData);
end if;
if b then 
  if vSelf  then 
    b:=ExchangeAnalyze.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  else 
    b:=Exchange.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  end if;
end if;

  b:= ExchangeAnalyze.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 4, b, vData);
end if;

begin 
declare
  l_Params        RPC.TypeGetInfoParams := RPC.GetInfoParams ();
  l_ResultArray   RPC.TypeResultArray;
  cPackage            constant varchar2(100) := 'UBRR_SAA_RPC';
  cGetClientDetailsEx constant varchar(30)   := 'GetClientDetailsEx';  --07.10.2005
  sEncoding           constant varchar(30)   := rpc.GetInfoParams().Encoding;
begin
  dbms_output.disable;--10.11.2017 Нестеров/Казакова. Отключение спула, т.к. падает онлайн-интерфейс
  if l_Params.InfoType in ('CreditChangePayCheck'
                         , 'CreditChangePayDateOffer'
                         , 'CreditChangePayDateAcpt'
                         , 'CreditChangePayCheckAll' 
                         , 'CreditChangePayDateOfferAll'
                         , 'CreditChangePayDateAcptAll'
                         -->> 19.02.2019 Юрин А.В. #59603
                         , 'CreditChangePayGetDcbo'
                         , 'CreditChangePayUpdateDcbo'
                         --<< 19.02.2019 Юрин А.В. #59603
                         ) then 
    ubrr_saa_ChangePay_rep.GetOffertForTelebank (l_Params, l_ResultArray);
    RPC.SetResultArray (l_ResultArray);
    :RET := 1;
  elsif l_Params.InfoType in ('ChangePhoneNumberCheck', 'ChangePhoneNumberOk') then
    ubrr_saa_phones.GetPhoneForTelebank(l_Params, l_ResultArray);
    RPC.SetResultArray (l_ResultArray);
    :RET := 1;
  -->> Скадовский А.А. 01.06.2018  17-1220
  elsif l_Params.InfoType in ('DBVNumberRequest') then
    ubrr_saa_dbv.GetDBVNumberRequest(l_Params, l_ResultArray);
    RPC.SetResultArray (l_ResultArray);
    :RET := 1;
  --<< Скадовский А.А. 01.06.2018  17-1220
  -->> Сенаторов С.А. 08.11.2019 19-66595
  elsif l_Params.InfoType in ('NACOPNumberRequest') then
    ubrr_nakop_acc.GetNAKOPNumberRequest(l_Params, l_ResultArray);
    RPC.SetResultArray (l_ResultArray);
    :RET := 1;
  -->> Сенаторов С.А. 08.11.2019 19-66595
  -->> Скадовский А.А. 11.05.2021 CREDCARD-495
  elsif l_Params.InfoType in ('GetClientDetailsEx') then
    -->> 21.05.2021  Скадовский А.А.  CREDCARD-558 GetClientDetailsEx корректировка запроса
    --GetClientDetailsEx (l_Params.Ident, l_Params.IdentType);
    ubrr_saa_rpc.GetClientDetailsEx (l_Params.Ident, l_Params.IdentType);
    --<< 21.05.2021  Скадовский А.А.  CREDCARD-558 GetClientDetailsEx корректировка запроса
    :RET := 1;
  --<< Скадовский А.А. 11.05.2021 CREDCARD-495
  -->> 01.09.2021  Скадовский А.А.  CREDCARD-539 3-10 Заказ справок в МБ
  elsif l_Params.InfoType in ('GetCloseCreditEx') then
    ubrr_saa_rpc.GetCloseCreditEx (l_Params.Ident, l_Params.IdentType);
    :RET := 1;
  --<< 01.09.2021  Скадовский А.А.  CREDCARD-539 3-10 Заказ справок в МБ
  -->> 28.10.2021  Скадовский А.А.  CREDCARD-775 разделение сообщений для мб
  elsif l_Params.InfoType in ('ProlongLimAcpt') then
    ubrr_saa_rpc.GetProlongLimAcpt (l_Params.Ident, l_Params.IdentType);
    :RET := 1;
  --<< 28.10.2021  Скадовский А.А.  CREDCARD-775 разделение сообщений для мб
  -->> 18.06.2021  Скадовский А.А.  CREDCARD-555
  elsif l_Params.InfoType in ('CreditCardProlLimOffer') then
    ubrr_saa_rpc.GetCreditCardProlLimOffer (l_Params.Ident, l_Params.IdentType);
    :RET := 1;
  --<< 18.06.2021  Скадовский А.А.  CREDCARD-555
  -->> 25.10.2021  Голенков А.А.  POTKRED-1117 Справка о выплаченных процентах в МБ
  elsif upper(l_Params.InfoType) in ('GETCONSCREDITINFO') then        
    ubrr_saa_rpc.GetConsCreditInfo(l_Params.Ident, l_Params.addparams);    
    :RET := 1;  
  --<< 25.10.2021  Голенков А.А.  POTKRED-1117 Справка о выплаченных процентах в МБ
  -->>01.03.2021  Коломиец Д.С.    POTKRED-373
  elsif upper(l_Params.InfoType) in ('CREDITINFO') then
    UBRR_STR_CREDITINFO.GetCreditInfoRequest(l_Params, l_ResultArray);
    if l_ResultArray.count != 0 then
      RPC.SetResultArray (l_ResultArray);
      :RET := 1;
    end if;
  elsif upper(l_Params.InfoType) in ('PAYMENTSCHEDULE') then
    UBRR_STR_CREDITINFO.GetScheduleInfoRequest(l_Params, l_ResultArray);
    if l_ResultArray.count != 0 then
      RPC.SetResultArray (l_ResultArray);
      :RET := 1;
    end if;
  elsif upper(l_Params.InfoType) in ('CONTRACTINFO') then
    UBRR_STR_CREDITINFO.GetContractInfoRequest(l_Params, l_ResultArray);
    if l_ResultArray.count != 0 then
      RPC.SetResultArray (l_ResultArray);
      :RET := 1;
    end if;
  --<<01.03.2021  Коломиец Д.С.    POTKRED-373
  end if;
end;
 null; end;

declare 
vOper OperKernel.TOper:=OperKernel.s_pOper; b boolean:=true; 
vObjType number := OperKernel.s_pObjType; 
vOperC    number := vOper.cOper; 
vData     varchar(3000) := OperKernel.s_pData; 
vSelf     boolean := OperKernel.s_pSelf; 
begin 
if vOper.evPre then 
  b:= ExchangeMEB.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 2, true, vData);
end if;
if b then 
  if vSelf  then 
    b:=ExchangeMEB.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  else 
    b:=Exchange.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  end if;
end if;
if vOper.evPost then 
  b:= ExchangeMEB.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 4, b, vData);
end if;
OperKernel.sBufBool:=b;
end;

  NUMBER) AS RATEVALUE, CAST (NULL AS NUMBER) AS RATEFACTOR, CAST (NULL AS 
  NUMBER) AS DEPENDENTONBASE 
FROM
 ( SELECT B.OPDATE CAPDATE, A.VALUE AMOUNT, B.DOCNO DOCNO, A.NO NO, 
  A.DEBITENTCODE DEBITENTCODE FROM TENTRY A, TDOCUMENT B WHERE A.BRANCH = 
  SEANCE.GETBRANCH AND A.CREDITACCOUNT = :B10 AND A.DEBITENTCODE IN (:B7 , 
  :B6 , :B5 , :B4 , :B3 , :B2 , :B1 ) AND B.BRANCH = A.BRANCH AND B.DOCNO = 
  A.DOCNO AND B.NEWDOCNO IS NULL AND ((:B9 IS NOT NULL AND B.OPDATE < :B9 ) 
  OR (:B9 IS NULL) ) AND ((:B8 IS NOT NULL AND :B8 < B.OPDATE) OR (:B8 IS 
  NULL) ) UNION ALL SELECT B.OPDATE CAPDATE, A.VALUE AMOUNT, B.DOCNO DOCNO,

  B.OPDATE) OR (:B8 IS NULL) ) UNION ALL SELECT B.OPDATE CAPDATE, A.VALUE

  A, TDOCUMENTARC B WHERE A.BRANCH = SEANCE.GETBRANCH AND A.CREDITACCOUNT = 
  :B10 AND A.DEBITENTCODE IN (:B7 , :B6 , :B5 , :B4 , :B3 , :B2 , :B1 ) AND

  AND :B8 < B.OPDATE) OR (:B8 IS NULL) ) UNION ALL SELECT B.OPDATE CAPDATE,

Select /*+
ORDERED
INDEX_DESC(e iEntry_CreditAccount)
USE_NL (e)
INDEX_DESC(d IDOCUMENTS_DOCNO)
USE_NL (d)
*/
 d.OpDate, e.DocNo, e.No, 0 ArcFlag
 From tEntry e, tDocument d
 Where e.Branch = :B And e.CreditAccount = :A And e.DocNo <= 4900325332 And e.Value >= .01
 And e.ValueDate Between nvl(:DF, e.ValueDate) And nvl(:DT, e.ValueDate)
 And d.Branch = e.Branch And d.DocNo = e.DocNo And d.NewDocNo is null
 And d.OpDate Between nvl(:DF, d.OpDate) And nvl(:DT, d.OpDate)
 UNION ALL Select /*+
ORDERED
INDEX_DESC(e iEntry_DebitAccount)
USE_NL (e)
INDEX_DESC(d IDOCUMENTS_DOCNO)
USE_NL (d)
*/
 d.OpDate, e.DocNo, e.No, 0 ArcFlag
 From tEntry e, tDocument d
 Where e.Branch = :B And e.DebitAccount = :A And e.DocNo <= 4900325332 And e.Value >= .01
 And e.ValueDate Between nvl(:DF, e.ValueDate) And nvl(:DT, e.ValueDate)
 And d.Branch = e.Branch And d.DocNo = e.DocNo And d.NewDocNo is null
 And d.OpDate Between nvl(:DF, d.OpDate) And nvl(:DT, d.OpDate)
 Order By 1 Desc, 2 Desc, 3 Desc

FROM
 ( SELECT /*+ cardinality(c 10) ordered use_nl(a b) index (a 
  iEntry_DebitAccount) */ B.OPDATE + NVL(:B3 , 0) AS OPDATE, -1 AS SIGN_, 
  A.ROWID AS ERW_ FROM TABLE(:B1 ) C, TENTRY A, TDOCUMENT B WHERE A.BRANCH = 
  :B4 AND A.DEBITACCOUNT = C.NAME AND B.BRANCH = A.BRANCH AND B.DOCNO = 
  A.DOCNO AND ((:B2 IS NOT NULL) AND (B.OPDATE + NVL(:B3 , 0) > :B2 ) OR (:B2 
  IS NULL) ) AND B.NEWDOCNO IS NULL UNION ALL SELECT /*+ cardinality(c 10) 
  ordered use_nl(a b) index (a iEntry_CreditAccount) */ B.OPDATE, 1 AS SIGN_,

  :B4 AND A.CREDITACCOUNT = C.NAME AND B.BRANCH = A.BRANCH AND B.DOCNO = 
  A.DOCNO AND ((:B2 IS NOT NULL) AND (B.OPDATE > :B2 ) OR (:B2 IS NULL) ) AND

begin

 Uamp.AddRec(Uamp.RT_PARAM, 'Echo', RPC.msgHeader.Echo, pAsEmpty => ''); 
 Uamp.AddRec(Uamp.RT_PARAM, 'TWRHI/Ver', RPC.msgHeader.ProductVersion, pAsEmpty => ''); 
 Uamp.AddRec(Uamp.RT_PARAM, 'Encoding', RPC.msgHeader.Encoding, pAsEmpty => '');

 Uamp.AddRec(Uamp.RT_PARAM, 'TWRHI/ResponseMsg', RPC.msgOut.ResponseMsg, pAsEmpty => ''); 
 Uamp.AddRec(Uamp.RT_PARAM, 'TWRHI/NextChallenge', RPC.msgOut_NextChallenge, pAsEmpty => '');

   if i = 1 and RPC.msgOut_GetInfo.Count = 1 then 
    Uamp.AddRec( Uamp.RT_PARAM,'TWRHI/GetInfo/Rp/Value', RPC.msgOut_GetInfo(i), pAsEmpty => '');

     Uamp.AddRec(case i when 1 then Uamp.RT_PARAM else Uamp.RT_VALUE_APPEND end,'TWRHI/GetInfo/Rp/Value', RPC.msgOut_GetInfo(i)); 
   end if;
 end loop; 
end;

Select /*+
ORDERED
INDEX_DESC(e iEntry_CreditAccount)
USE_NL (e)
INDEX_DESC(d IDOCUMENTS_DOCNO)
USE_NL (d)
*/
 d.OpDate, e.DocNo, e.No, 0 ArcFlag
 From tEntry e, tDocument d
 Where e.Branch = :B And e.CreditAccount = :A And e.DocNo <= 4900532628 And e.Value >= .01
 And e.ValueDate Between nvl(:DF, e.ValueDate) And nvl(:DT, e.ValueDate)
 And d.Branch = e.Branch And d.DocNo = e.DocNo And d.NewDocNo is null
 And d.OpDate Between nvl(:DF, d.OpDate) And nvl(:DT, d.OpDate)
 UNION ALL Select /*+
ORDERED
INDEX_DESC(e iEntry_DebitAccount)
USE_NL (e)
INDEX_DESC(d IDOCUMENTS_DOCNO)
USE_NL (d)
*/
 d.OpDate, e.DocNo, e.No, 0 ArcFlag
 From tEntry e, tDocument d
 Where e.Branch = :B And e.DebitAccount = :A And e.DocNo <= 4900532628 And e.Value >= .01
 And e.ValueDate Between nvl(:DF, e.ValueDate) And nvl(:DT, e.ValueDate)
 And d.Branch = e.Branch And d.DocNo = e.DocNo And d.NewDocNo is null
 And d.OpDate Between nvl(:DF, d.OpDate) And nvl(:DT, d.OpDate)
 Order By 1 Desc, 2 Desc, 3 Desc

declare
 vIx pls_integer;
 i pls_integer;
 vArrayEnd Uamp.TRecordType;
 vName varchar(250);
 vValue varchar(32767);
 procedure say(ptxt varchar) is begin UAMP.say('Script_IN: '||ptxt);end;
begin 
  vIx := Uamp.saRecord.First; 
  vArrayEnd := Uamp.RT_END_ARRAY;

  RPC.msgHeader.Version := Null;
  RPC.msgHeader.Echo := Null;
  RPC.msgHeader.ProductVersion := Null;
  RPC.msgHeader.Encoding := Null;
  RPC.msgIn.Product := Null;
  RPC.msgIn.Operation := Null;
  RPC.msgIn.OperationOld := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.Account := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn_AttrList.delete;
  RPC.msgStmIn.RefreshPackNo := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.FromTime := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.ToTime := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.MaxCount := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.PAN := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.MBR := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.OperCode := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn_OperType.delete;
  RPC.msgStmIn.FromAmount := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.ToAmount := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.FrontId := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.BackId := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.OperDate := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.OrigCurrency := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.BackAccount := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.CardOnly := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.Language := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.TranPAN := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.TranMBR := Null;
  RPC.msgStmIn.UseLinkCards := Null;
  RPC.msgATMCntrIn.Ident := Null;
  RPC.msgATMCntrIn.IdentType := Null;
  RPC.msgATMCntrIn.ReqType := Null;
  RPC.msgATMCntrIn.AddParams.delete;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInfo.Ident := Null;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInfo.IdentType := Null;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInfo.InfoType := Null;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInfo.Format := Null;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInfo.TextSeparator := Null;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInfo.AddParams := Null;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.InstallmentPlan := Null;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.InstallmentPlanIndex := Null;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.PaymentTerm := Null;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.TermName := Null;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.RetailerName := Null;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.RetailerFIID := Null;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.Amount := Null;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.Currency := Null;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.PAN := Null;
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.MBR := Null;

  while( vIx is not null ) loop 
    vName := Uamp.saRecord(vIx).Name;
    vVAlue := Uamp.saRecord(vIx).Value;

    if( vName = 'Ver' ) then 
  RPC.msgHeader.Version := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'Echo' ) then 
  RPC.msgHeader.Echo := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/Ver' ) then 
  RPC.msgHeader.ProductVersion := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'Encoding' ) then 
  RPC.msgHeader.Encoding := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'Product' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn.Product := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/Operation' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn.Operation := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'Operation' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn.OperationOld := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/Acct' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.Account := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/AttrList' ) then 
      if( Uamp.saRecord(vIx).RecordType = Uamp.RT_BEGIN_STRUCT ) then 
        vArrayEnd := Uamp.RT_END_STRUCT;
      elsif( Uamp.saRecord(vIx).RecordType = Uamp.rt_Param ) then 
        vArrayEnd := Uamp.RT_END_ARRAY;
      else
        UAMP.Next(vIx);  /* skip BEGIN_ARRAY */ 
        vArrayEnd := Uamp.RT_END_ARRAY;
      end if;
      i := 1;
      RPC.msgStmIn_AttrList.Delete();
      while((vIx is not null) and ( Uamp.saRecord(vIx).RecordType != vArrayEnd) ) loop
        RPC.msgStmIn_AttrList(i) := Uamp.saRecord(vIx).Value; 
        UAMP.Next(vIx);
        i := i + 1;
        if( (vIx is not null) and (Uamp.saRecord(vIx-1).RecordType = Uamp.rt_Param) ) then 
           exit; /* one-string array detected */
        end if; 
      end loop;
      if ( (vIx is not null) and (Uamp.saRecord(vIx).RecordType = vArrayEnd)) then UAMP.Next(vIx);end if;   /* skip END_ARRAY whatever it is */

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/RefreshPackNo' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.RefreshPackNo := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/FromTime' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.FromTime := Uamp.From1900StrToDate(vValue); 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/ToTime' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.ToTime := Uamp.From1900StrToDate(vValue); 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/MaxCount' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.MaxCount := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/PAN' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.PAN := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/MBR' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.MBR := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/OperCode' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.OperCode := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/OperType' ) then 
      if( Uamp.saRecord(vIx).RecordType = Uamp.RT_BEGIN_STRUCT ) then 
        vArrayEnd := Uamp.RT_END_STRUCT;
      elsif( Uamp.saRecord(vIx).RecordType = Uamp.rt_Param ) then 
        vArrayEnd := Uamp.RT_END_ARRAY;
      else
        UAMP.Next(vIx);  /* skip BEGIN_ARRAY */ 
        vArrayEnd := Uamp.RT_END_ARRAY;
      end if;
      i := 1;
      RPC.msgStmIn_OperType.Delete();
      while((vIx is not null) and ( Uamp.saRecord(vIx).RecordType != vArrayEnd) ) loop
        RPC.msgStmIn_OperType(i) := Uamp.saRecord(vIx).Value; 
        UAMP.Next(vIx);
        i := i + 1;
        if( (vIx is not null) and (Uamp.saRecord(vIx-1).RecordType = Uamp.rt_Param) ) then 
           exit; /* one-string array detected */
        end if; 
      end loop;
      if ( (vIx is not null) and (Uamp.saRecord(vIx).RecordType = vArrayEnd)) then UAMP.Next(vIx);end if;   /* skip END_ARRAY whatever it is */

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/FromAmount' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.FromAmount := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/ToAmount' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.ToAmount := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/FrontId' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.FrontId := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/BackId' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.BackId := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/OperDate' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.OperDate := Uamp.From1900StrToDate(vValue); 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/OrigCurrency' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.OrigCurrency := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/BackAccount' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.BackAccount := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/CardOnly' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.CardOnly := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/Language' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.Language := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/TranPAN' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.TranPAN := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/TranMBR' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.TranMBR := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rq/UseLinkCards' ) then 
  RPC.msgStmIn.UseLinkCards := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/ATMGetContractInfo/Rq/ContractIdent' ) then 
  RPC.msgATMCntrIn.Ident := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/ATMGetContractInfo/Rq/IdentType' ) then 
  RPC.msgATMCntrIn.IdentType := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/ATMGetContractInfo/Rq/ReqType' ) then 
  RPC.msgATMCntrIn.ReqType := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/ATMGetContractInfo/Rq/AddParams' ) then 
      declare i pls_integer:=1; begin 
      RPC.msgATMCntrIn.AddParams(i) := Uamp.saRecord(vIx).Value; 
      UAMP.Next(vix,false); i:=i+1;
      while (vIx is not null) and (UAMP.saRecord(vix).RecordType=UAMP.RT_VALUE_APPEND) loop
        RPC.msgATMCntrIn.AddParams(i) := Uamp.saRecord(vIx).Value; 
        UAMP.Next(vix,false); i:=i+1;
      end loop;
      end;

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInfo/Rq/Ident' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInfo.Ident := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInfo/Rq/IdentType' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInfo.IdentType := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInfo/Rq/InfoType' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInfo.InfoType := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInfo/Rq/Format' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInfo.Format := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInfo/Rq/TextSeparator' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInfo.TextSeparator := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInfo/Rq/AddParams' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInfo.AddParams := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInstallmentData/Rq/InstallmentPlan' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.InstallmentPlan := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInstallmentData/Rq/InstallmentPlanIndex' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.InstallmentPlanIndex := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInstallmentData/Rq/PaymentTerm' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.PaymentTerm := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInstallmentData/Rq/TermName' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.TermName := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInstallmentData/Rq/RetailerName' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.RetailerName := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInstallmentData/Rq/RetailerFIID' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.RetailerFIID := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInstallmentData/Rq/Amount' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.Amount := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInstallmentData/Rq/Currency' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.Currency := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInstallmentData/Rq/PAN' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.PAN := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInstallmentData/Rq/MBR' ) then 
  RPC.msgIn_GetInstallmentData.MBR := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    else
      say('skipping field: ' || vName);
      UAMP.Next(vIx);    /*skip it*/
    end if;

  end loop;
exception when others then
    s.err('vix='||vix||', name = '||Vname||',val='||vValue);
    raise;
end;

DECLARE
  cursor c1 is
  SELECT A.ExtID,A.Type, A.pType, A.Active, D.ValueStr,D.ValueNum, D.ValueDate, D.ValueXML,
         (select description from Tobjaddpropreference r 
            where NVL(A.isListVal,0) = 0
              and r.branch = d.branch and r.propid = d.propid 
              and (NVL(r.valuestr,'~') = NVL(d.valuestr,'~')) 
              and (Nvl(r.valuenum,-999) = Nvl(d.valuenum,-999))
              and rownum =1 ) 
         as Description 
  FROM tObjAdditionalProperty A 
     left outer join tObjAddPropData_ACCOUNT d 
       on d.branch = a.branch and d.propid = a.id 
          and d.ownerid = ObjUserPropertyKernel.sCursorParam_OWNERID
  WHERE A.Branch = ObjUserPropertyKernel.sCursorParam_BRANCH 
    and A.ObjectID = ObjUserPropertyKernel.sCursorParam_OBJECT.Type
    and A.ObjSubType = ObjUserPropertyKernel.sCursorParam_OBJECT.SubType;
  vRet ApiTypes.TypeUserPropList;
  vIndex number;
  vUseFilter boolean := false;
BEGIN
   vIndex:=0;
   vUseFilter := ObjUserPropertyKernel.sCursorParam_Filter.Count()>0;
   for crow in c1 loop
     if (ObjUserPropertyKernel.sCursorParam_IncludeNulls 
         or not(crow.valueNum is null and crow.ValueStr is null 
                and crow.ValueDate is null and crow.ValueXML is null)
        ) 
        and 
        (not vUseFilter or ObjUserPropertyKernel.sCursorParam_Filter.Exists(crow.ExtID) )
        and 
        (not ObjUserPropertyKernel.sCursorParam_OnlyActive or crow.Active = 1)
     then
       vIndex:=vIndex+1;
       vRet(vIndex).ID        := crow.ExtID;
       vRet(vIndex).FieldType := crow.Type;
       vRet(vIndex).pType     := crow.pType;
       vRet(vIndex).ValueStr  := crow.ValueStr;
       vRet(vIndex).ValueNum  := crow.ValueNum;
       vRet(vIndex).ValueDate := crow.ValueDate;
       vRet(vIndex).ValueXML  := crow.ValueXML;
       vRet(vIndex).ValueText := crow.Description;
     end if;
   end loop;
   ObjUserPropertyKernel.sRec:=vRet;
END;

call     count       cpu    elapsed       disk      query    current        rows
------- ------  -------- ---------- ---------- ---------- ----------  ----------
Parse        1      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0
Execute     53      0.00       0.02          0          6          0          53
Fetch        0      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0
------- ------  -------- ---------- ---------- ---------- ----------  ----------
total       54      0.00       0.02          0          6          0          53

Misses in library cache during parse: 0
Optimizer mode: RULE
Parsing user id: 64     (recursive depth: 4)

declare 
vOper OperKernel.TOper:=OperKernel.s_pOper; b boolean:=true; 
vObjType number := OperKernel.s_pObjType; 
vOperC    number := vOper.cOper; 
vData     varchar(3000) := OperKernel.s_pData; 
vSelf     boolean := OperKernel.s_pSelf; 
begin 
if vOper.evPre then 
  b:= ExchangeFrontOffice.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 2, true, vData);
end if;
if b then 
  if vSelf  then 
    b:=ExchangeFrontOffice.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  else 
    b:=Exchange.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  end if;
end if;
if vOper.evPost then 
  b:= ExchangeFrontOffice.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 4, b, vData);
end if;
OperKernel.sBufBool:=b;
end;

declare 
vOper OperKernel.TOper:=OperKernel.s_pOper; b boolean:=true; 
vObjType number := OperKernel.s_pObjType; 
vOperC    number := vOper.cOper; 
vData     varchar(3000) := OperKernel.s_pData; 
vSelf     boolean := OperKernel.s_pSelf; 
begin 
if vOper.evPre then 
  b:= EXABAU.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 2, true, vData);
end if;
if b then 
  if vSelf  then 
    b:=EXABAU.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  else 
    b:=Exchange.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  end if;
end if;
if vOper.evPost then 
  b:= EXABAU.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 4, b, vData);
end if;
OperKernel.sBufBool:=b;
end;

call     count       cpu    elapsed       disk      query    current        rows
------- ------  -------- ---------- ---------- ---------- ----------  ----------

declare
 vIx pls_integer;
 i pls_integer;
 vArrayEnd Uamp.TRecordType;
 vName varchar(250);
 vValue varchar(32767);
 procedure say(ptxt varchar) is begin UAMP.say('Script_IN: '||ptxt);end;
begin 
  vIx := Uamp.saRecord.First; 
  vArrayEnd := Uamp.RT_END_ARRAY;

  RPC.msgHeader.Version := Null;
  RPC.msgHeader.Echo := Null;
  RPC.msgHeader.ProductVersion := Null;
  RPC.msgHeader.Encoding := Null;
  RPC.msgOut.Response := Null;
  RPC.msgOut.ResponseMsg := Null;
  RPC.msgOut_NextChallenge := Null;
  RPC.msgOut_GetInfo.delete;

  while( vIx is not null ) loop 
    vName := Uamp.saRecord(vIx).Name;
    vVAlue := Uamp.saRecord(vIx).Value;

    if( vName = 'Ver' ) then 
  RPC.msgHeader.Version := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'Echo' ) then 
  RPC.msgHeader.Echo := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/Ver' ) then 
  RPC.msgHeader.ProductVersion := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'Encoding' ) then 
  RPC.msgHeader.Encoding := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/Response' ) then 
  RPC.msgOut.Response := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/ResponseMsg' ) then 
  RPC.msgOut.ResponseMsg := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/NextChallenge' ) then 
  RPC.msgOut_NextChallenge := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetInfo/Rp/Value' ) then 
      declare i pls_integer:=1; begin 
      RPC.msgOut_GetInfo(i) := Uamp.saRecord(vIx).Value; 
      UAMP.Next(vix,false); i:=i+1;
      while (vIx is not null) and (UAMP.saRecord(vix).RecordType=UAMP.RT_VALUE_APPEND) loop
        RPC.msgOut_GetInfo(i) := Uamp.saRecord(vIx).Value; 
        UAMP.Next(vix,false); i:=i+1;
      end loop;
      end;

    else
      say('skipping field: ' || vName);
      UAMP.Next(vIx);    /*skip it*/
    end if;

  end loop;
exception when others then
    s.err('vix='||vix||', name = '||Vname||',val='||vValue);
    raise;
end;

call     count       cpu    elapsed       disk      query    current        rows
------- ------  -------- ---------- ---------- ---------- ----------  ----------
Parse       53      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0
Execute      0      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0
Fetch        0      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0
------- ------  -------- ---------- ---------- ---------- ----------  ----------
total       53      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0

Misses in library cache during parse: 0
Optimizer mode: RULE
Parsing user id: 64     (recursive depth: 2)

declare 
vOper OperKernel.TOper:=OperKernel.s_pOper; b boolean:=true; 
vObjType number := OperKernel.s_pObjType; 
vOperC    number := vOper.cOper; 
vData     varchar(3000) := OperKernel.s_pData; 
vSelf     boolean := OperKernel.s_pSelf; 
begin 
if vOper.evPre then 
  b:= Europay.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 2, true, vData);
end if;
if b then 
  if vSelf  then 
    b:=Europay.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  else 
    b:=Exchange.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  end if;
end if;
if vOper.evPost then 
  b:= Europay.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 4, b, vData);
end if;
OperKernel.sBufBool:=b;
end;

declare 
vOper OperKernel.TOper:=OperKernel.s_pOper; b boolean:=true; 
vObjType number := OperKernel.s_pObjType; 
vOperC    number := vOper.cOper; 
vData     varchar(3000) := OperKernel.s_pData; 
vSelf     boolean := OperKernel.s_pSelf; 
begin 
if vOper.evPre then 
  b:= UnionCard.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 2, true, vData);
end if;
if b then 
  if vSelf  then 
    b:=UnionCard.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  else 
    b:=Exchange.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  end if;
end if;
if vOper.evPost then 
  b:= UnionCard.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 4, b, vData);
end if;
OperKernel.sBufBool:=b;
end;

call     count       cpu    elapsed       disk      query    current        rows
------- ------  -------- ---------- ---------- ---------- ----------  ----------
Parse        1      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0
Execute      1      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           1
Fetch        0      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0
------- ------  -------- ---------- ---------- ---------- ----------  ----------
total        2      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           1

  PERIODCRDDAYS, MAX (CASE WHEN NAME = 'PERIODCRDMONTH' THEN B.NVALUE ELSE 
  NULL END) AS PERIODCRDMONTH, MAX (CASE WHEN NAME = 'TYPEPERIODCRD' THEN 
  B.NVALUE ELSE NULL END) AS TYPEPERIODCRD, MAX (CASE WHEN NAME = 
  'PERIODPRCDAYS' THEN B.NVALUE ELSE NULL END) AS PERIODPRCDAYS, MAX (CASE 
  WHEN NAME = 'PERIODPRCMONTH' THEN B.NVALUE ELSE NULL END) AS PERIODPRCMONTH,

declare

  b:= ExchangeMBbranch.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 4, b, vData);
end if;

declare
 vIx pls_integer;
 i pls_integer;
 vArrayEnd Uamp.TRecordType;
 vName varchar(250);
 vValue varchar(32767);
 procedure say(ptxt varchar) is begin UAMP.say('Script_IN: '||ptxt);end;
begin 
  vIx := Uamp.saRecord.First; 
  vArrayEnd := Uamp.RT_END_ARRAY;

  RPC.msgHeader.Version := Null;
  RPC.msgHeader.Echo := Null;
  RPC.msgHeader.ProductVersion := Null;
  RPC.msgHeader.Encoding := Null;
  RPC.msgOut.Response := Null;
  RPC.msgOut.ResponseMsg := Null;
  RPC.msgOut_NextChallenge := Null;
  RPC.msgStmOutList.delete;

  while( vIx is not null ) loop 
    vName := Uamp.saRecord(vIx).Name;
    vVAlue := Uamp.saRecord(vIx).Value;

    if( vName = 'Ver' ) then 
  RPC.msgHeader.Version := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'Echo' ) then 
  RPC.msgHeader.Echo := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/Ver' ) then 
  RPC.msgHeader.ProductVersion := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'Encoding' ) then 
  RPC.msgHeader.Encoding := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/Response' ) then 
  RPC.msgOut.Response := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/ResponseMsg' ) then 
  RPC.msgOut.ResponseMsg := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/NextChallenge' ) then 
  RPC.msgOut_NextChallenge := vValue; 
  UAMP.Next(vIx);

    elsif( vName = 'TWRHI/GetStatement/Rp/List' ) then 
      if( Uamp.saRecord(vIx).RecordType = Uamp.RT_BEGIN_STRUCT ) then 
        vArrayEnd := Uamp.RT_END_STRUCT;
      elsif( Uamp.saRecord(vIx).RecordType = Uamp.rt_Param ) then 
        vArrayEnd := Uamp.RT_END_ARRAY;
      else
        UAMP.Next(vIx);  /* skip BEGIN_ARRAY */ 
        vArrayEnd := Uamp.RT_END_ARRAY;
      end if;
      i := 1;
      RPC.msgStmOutList.Delete();
      while((vIx is not null) and ( Uamp.saRecord(vIx).RecordType != vArrayEnd) ) loop
  RPC.msgStmOutList(i) := Null;
  UAMP.Next(vIx); /* skip BEGIN_STRUCT */ 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).FrontId := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).BackId := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).OperDate := Uamp.From1900StrToDate(UAMP.field(vIx)); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).Code := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).Amount := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).Description := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).Type := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).TranTime := Uamp.From1900StrToDate(UAMP.field(vIx)); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).PAN := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).MBR := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).TermClass := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).TermName := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).TermLocation := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).TermSIC := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).OrigAmount := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).OrigCurrency := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).AnotherTitle := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).BackAccount := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).BackAmount := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).Remain := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).Approval := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).Currency := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).Account := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).RetailerName := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).FullRemark := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).AcctImpactList := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).TermCity := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).TermCountry := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).ExtPSData := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).ArrestImpactInd := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).ArrestImpact := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      RPC.msgStmOutList(i).MessToRecipient := UAMP.field(vIx); 
      while (vIx is not null) and ( Uamp.saRecord(vIx).RecordType = Uamp.RT_STRUCT_FIELD ) loop 
        say('WARNING! UAMP.ParseData : unknown field : val = '||s.maskdata(Uamp.saRecord(vIx).Value));   
        UAMP.Next(vIx);                     /* skip unknow fields */ 
      end loop; 
      if( vArrayEnd != Uamp.RT_END_STRUCT ) then 
        UAMP.Next(vIx);                              /* skip END_STRUCT */ 
      end if;
        i := i + 1;
        if( (vIx is not null) and (Uamp.saRecord(vIx-1).RecordType = Uamp.rt_Param) ) then 
           exit; /* one-string array detected */
        end if; 
      end loop;
      if ( (vIx is not null) and (Uamp.saRecord(vIx).RecordType = vArrayEnd)) then UAMP.Next(vIx);end if;   /* skip END_ARRAY whatever it is */

    else
      say('skipping field: ' || vName);
      UAMP.Next(vIx);    /*skip it*/
    end if;

  end loop;
exception when others then
    s.err('vix='||vix||', name = '||Vname||',val='||vValue);
    raise;
end;

call     count       cpu    elapsed       disk      query    current        rows

Parse       20      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0
Execute      0      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0
Fetch        0      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0

total       20      0.00       0.00          0          0          0           0

declare 
vOper OperKernel.TOper:=OperKernel.s_pOper; b boolean:=true; 
vObjType number := OperKernel.s_pObjType; 
vOperC    number := vOper.cOper; 
vData     varchar(3000) := OperKernel.s_pData; 
vSelf     boolean := OperKernel.s_pSelf; 
begin 
if vOper.evPre then 
  b:= BMSExchange.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 2, true, vData);
end if;
if b then 
  if vSelf  then 
    b:=BMSExchange.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  else 
    b:=Exchange.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 1, b, vData);
  end if;
end if;
if vOper.evPost then 
  b:= BMSExchange.Oper(vObjType, vOperC, 4, b, vData);
end if;
OperKernel.sBufBool:=b;
end;

call     count       cpu    elapsed       disk      query    current        rows

declare n varchar(164); begin
 n:=ExchangeVisa.sRow.TCR0; ExchangeVisa.sRow90.ProcessingBIN:=RTrim(substr(n,1,6)); 
ExchangeVisa.sRow90.ProcessingDate:=FormGen.todate(rtrim(substr(n,7,5)),'YYDDD'); 
ExchangeVisa.sRow90.Reserved1:=RTrim(substr(n,12,6)); 
ExchangeVisa.sRow90.SettlementDate:=FormGen.todate(rtrim(substr(n,18,5)),'YYDDD'); 
ExchangeVisa.sRow90.Reserved2:=RTrim(substr(n,23,2)); 
ExchangeVisa.sRow90.ReleaseNumber:=RTrim(substr(n,25,3)); 
ExchangeVisa.sRow90.TestOption:=RTrim(substr(n,28,4)); 
ExchangeVisa.sRow90.Reserved3:=RTrim(substr(n,32,29)); 
ExchangeVisa.sRow90.SecurityCode:=RTrim(substr(n,61,8)); 
ExchangeVisa.sRow90.Reserved4:=RTrim(substr(n,69,6)); 
ExchangeVisa.sRow90.IncomingFileID:=RTrim(substr(n,75,3)); 
ExchangeVisa.sRow90.Reserved5:=RTrim(substr(n,78,87)); 
exception when OTHERS then s.err('ReadCursor3'); raise; end;
